@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vbtpwz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(0.96)
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.34 / v0 + 0.68)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.41 + tmp + 0.82)))
    v0 = (tmp - tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
